console.log(z); // 0 (fallback default applied because z was undefined)`,exercises:[{id:"coords-extractor",title:"Fallback Coordinate Deconstructor",difficulty:"Warm-up",codeSnippet:`// Example Use Case: Extracting coordinates with fallback assignments
